wiki.summary: "High and Dry" by Jamie Cullum is a cover of Radiohead's "High and Dry"

track.name: High And Dry
comments: I saw him live. Greatest concert in my life. Front row. I got a high five from him.
This is pretty good. He has a good sound. A lot of passion in his voice - not forced.
Never heard the original but I love this song! Very soulful.
man who is this kid! He keeps on popping up and I keep on liking it lol
There are some things I like better about this version than the original...
His songs are so relaxing, great artist.
It's not about being better than the original, it's a whole different thing! Just relaxing...
I like how he's not made a 'clone' of the original. This is how covers should be done!!

chaval, deja tranquilos a los dioses!
qué lástima de juventud...
